item.title: CVE-2023-25586|2023-09-14T20:49:15.468Z -- fedora -- fedora%2036
item.description: A flaw was found in Binutils. A logic fail in the bfd_init_section_decompress_status function may lead to the use of an uninitialized variable that can cause a crash and local denial of service.
